message.body: Hey Julia, Brenna's horse didn't pass the vet :( I want to give her a lesson tomorrow, do you want to let her have one on lucky? It's TOTALLY fine if no, just thought I'd ask because I know u mentioned her riding him possibly. :)
Boo! Yes, no problem if she wants to borrow lucky today. (Or tomorrow if it's too short notice, I just saw this!)
Ok! I will let her know and I'll give her lesson today on him. At 10 :) thx!
